    dc:title "First record of the genus Stenotus Jakovlev from Australia, with two new species, and a list of mirine species from Witchelina Nature Reserve (Insecta: Heteroptera: Miridae: Mirinae: Mirini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196468>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196470>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196474>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196478>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196490>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196480> ;
