<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196468>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Habitus view of Stenotus gressitti, Stenotus witchelina and Stenotus binotatus (male and female of each species)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196468/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196470>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Scanning electron micrographs. Stenotus gressitti: (A) head of male, anterior view; (B) head and pronotum of male, dorsal view; (E) head and pronotum of female, lateral view; (I) vestiture on hemelytra. Stenotus witchelina: (C) head and pronotum of male, dorsal view; (D) head of male, anterior view; (F) head and pronotum of female, lateral view; (G) head of female, anterior view; (H) head of female, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196470/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196474>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Scanning electron micrographs. Stenotus gressitti: (A) hind tarsus; (C) pretarsus, lateral view; (D) abdomen, lateral view; (F) pretarsus, dorsal view; (G) pretarsus, ventral view; (H) evaporatorium. Stenotus witchelina: (B) hind tarsus; (E) abdomen, lateral view; (I) evaporatorium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196478>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Male genitalia. Stenotus gressitti: (A) inflated aedeagus, dorsal view; (B) right paramere, dorsal view; (C) left paramere, posterior view; (D) left paramere, dorsal view; (E) genital capsule, dorsal view. Stenotus witchelina: (F) inflated aedeagus, dorsal view; (G) right paramere, dorsal view; (H) left paramere, posterior view; (I) left paramere, dorsal view; (J) genital capsule, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196490>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Female genitalia. Stenotus gressitti: (A) dorsal labiate plate; (D) posterior wall of bursa copulatrix. Stenotus witchelina: (B) dorsal labiate plate; (E) posterior wall of bursa copulatrix. Stenotus binotatus: (C) dorsal labiate plate; (F) posterior wall of bursa copulatrix." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196490/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5196480>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Male genitalia. Stenotus binotatus: (A) inflated aedeagus, dorsal view; (B) right paramere, dorsal view; (C) left paramere, posterior view; (D) left paramere, dorsal view; (E) genital capsule, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5196480/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

